          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>honey</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic </strong>(not a fan of raw garlic? Just add a little!), a very generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in small bowl – this is your <strong>honey</strong> <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
